IHStoRGB - Class in plugins
This tool transforms three intensity, hue, and saturation (IHS; sometimes HSI or HIS) images raster images into three equivalent multispectral images corresponding with the red, green, and blue channels of an RGB composite.

ImageRectification - Class in plugins
This tool is used to perform image-to-map rectification i.e., transform the geometric properties of an image to match that of a projected map, or image-to-image registration.
